# Shared package

Owner: **contracts**. No React, no engine imports.

## cards.json

- Path: `src/data/cards.json`
- JSON `type` field = archetype; engine sets `asset` | `event`
- Do not rename `id` without migration task
- Validate JSON before finishing

## types.ts

`GameState` shape changes require same-task updates in `game-engine` + `apps/web`.

## Helpers

`canPay`, clamps, `describeCardEffectBullets` — use from here, do not duplicate in web.

## Build

`npm run build -w @all-according-to-plan/shared` after changes.

## Forbidden

- Importing `game-engine` or `apps/web`
- Game transition logic in utils
